    <article class="article">
      <header class="article-header">
        <h1 title="I want to use lyrics within my novel" class="article-title">
          I want to use lyrics within my novel
          
        </h1>

        
      </header>

      <section class="article-info">
        <div class="article-content">
          <div class="article-body"><p>pixiv does not have a usage contract with JASRAC or any other international society for authors' copyrights.<br>If we confirm that you've used lyrics in your work that were written by someone else, <br>in addition to sending you a warning message, we may ask that you edit or adjust the privacy settings of your work.</p>
<p><a href="https://policies.pixiv.net/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Terms of Use</a><br>Prohibited Conduct<br>・Conduct that infringes or is likely to infringe on the copyrights, design rights or other Intellectual Property Rights (defined in Article 22, Paragraph 1) of the Company or third parties</p>
<p>Based on the above terms, we must ask that you refrain from using the work of another without permission.</p></div>

          <div class="article-attachments">
            <ul class="attachments">
              
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

